headline: Clean-Energy Companies Brace for Whiplash From ‘Big, Beautiful Bill’
summary: $500 billion That's the approximate fall in investment in electricity and clean fuels production by 2035 that will result from President Trump’s “big, beautiful bill,” according to estimates from a Princeton University-led project.
